  <body>
    <segment id="1">
Deficit</segment>
    <segment id="14" parent="26" relname="span">

So far, the planned deselection of Kyritz mayor Bärbel Stewin has been a relatively clear matter.</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="24" relname="preparation">  

The facts:</segment>
    <segment id="15" parent="19" relname="conjunction"> 

Over 850 residents sign petitions</segment>
    <segment id="16" parent="19" relname="conjunction"> 

and urge the city council members to initiate the recall petition.</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="20" relname="conjunction">  

They do as they are told,</segment>
    <segment id="17" parent="20" relname="conjunction"> 

and vote on it six weeks later.</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="21" relname="preparation">  

The result is known.</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="21" relname="span">  

Without exception, people are in favor of calling for a referendum.</segment>
    <segment id="6" parent="5" relname="result">  

The vote will take place on January 13th.</segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="27" relname="preparation">

And now?</segment>
    <segment id="13" parent="27" relname="span">  

Now there are first voices rising, demanding that one please clearly state why Mrs. Stewin is considered no longer suitable to manage the city.</segment>
    <segment id="8" parent="13" relname="elaboration"> 

It is not enough to confirm a reciprocal imbalance.</segment>
    <segment id="9" parent="30" relname="conjunction">

Today, the FDP local chairman Kai Müller from Kyritz supports the decision of the city councillors from November 14 </segment>
    <segment id="18" parent="30" relname="conjunction"> 

and issues a call to the public.</segment>
    <segment id="10" parent="33" relname="joint"> 

Every resident of Kyritz should inform themselves of the facts that make a dismissal inevitable from their perspective from the representatives.</segment>
    <segment id="11" parent="34" relname="span">  

However, educational work in a one-to-one conversation is difficult to imagine.</segment>
    <segment id="12" parent="32" relname="sequence">  

The voter wants to be fully informed,</segment>
    <segment id="31" parent="32" relname="sequence"> 

before they have the final say.</segment>
<group id="19" type="multinuc" parent="24" relname="sequence" />
